Text:
As you guys read this please keep in mind that it is really easy to upgrade from slower xeon w35xx processors as the single-quads use standard oem intel processors with integrated heat spreaders, while the duals are LIDLESS and its much harder to upgrade those.

Just to give you an idea.. I followed this guide and upgraded my 2.66 w3520 to the most powerful 3.33 or w3580 processor. Really simple and easy.
